        "text": "士兵收了錢，就照著祭司長和長老的指使去作。這種說法直到今日還流傳在猶太人當中。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "兵丁受了銀錢，就照所囑咐他們的去行。這話就傳說在猶太人中間，直到今日。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "And they took the money and did as they had been instructed; and this story was widely spread among the Jews, and is to this day."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "So the soldiers took the money and did as they were instructed. And this story has been widely circulated among the Jews to this very day."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "So the guards accepted the bribe and said what they were told to say. Their story spread widely among the Jews, and they still tell it today."
      }
    },
